sec.p:
The following procedures will be completed at this visit:
The actigraphy devices will be collected from the participants;
The online or paper sleep diaries will be reviewed and/or collected;
The dialysis shift days and the dialysis shift start time for each study participant will be noted;
The case-report form on cumulative weekly use of sedatives/hypnotics and opiates will be completed, assessing the use of sleep aids for the preceding 7 nights.
The participants will be scheduled to receive a phone call for the baseline Computer-Assisted Telephone Interviewing (CATI).
